      "raw": "Monday: 10:00 AM – 6:00 PM | Tuesday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM | Wednesday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM | Thursday: 10:00 AM – 8:00 PM | Friday: 9:00 AM – 6:00 PM | Saturday: Closed | Sunday: Closed",
